"before each" hook
request: GET, /api/v1/plano-de-contas/tipo-procedimento
assert: expected **200** to equal **200**
assert: expected **[ Array(3) ]** to be an array
assert: expected **3** to be above **0**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipo, ...) }** to have property **id**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipo, ...) }** to have property **id** of **1**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipo, ...) }** to have property **tipo**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipo, ...) }** to have property **tipo** of **null**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipo, ...) }** to have property **categoria**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipo, ...) }** to have property **categoria** of **null**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipo, ...) }** to have property **subPrimaria**
assert: expected **{ Object (codigo, nome) }** to deeply equal **{ Object (codigo, nome) }**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipo, ...) }** to have property **subSecundaria**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipo, ...) }** to have property **subSecundaria** of **null**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipo, ...) }** to have property **classificacao**
assert: expected **{ Object (codigo, nome) }** to deeply equal **{ Object (codigo, nome) }**
